| Property | Attribute | Description            | Type     | Default     |
| -------- | --------- | ---------------------- | -------- | ----------- |

| `height` | `height`  | icon height (optional) | `number` | `undefined` |
| `iconid` | `iconid`  | icon id (optional)     | `string` | `undefined` |

| `width`  | `width`   | icon width (optional)  | `number` | `undefined` |
